public class TrafficAreaType
extends _TransportationObjectType

Type describing the class for traffic Areas. Traffic areas are the surfaces where traffic actually takes place. As subclass of _CityObject, a TrafficArea inherits all attributes and relations, in particular an id, names, external references, generic attributes and generalization relations.
